[normal]got 
[normal]some grip on it, 
[normal]is
[normal] only meeting, I think, 64% for their four
[normal]&#x2011;
[normal]hour target and only 29% for four
[normal]&#x2011;
[normal]hour admissions
[normal],
[normal] and their ambition is to hit 90% by the end of 2016. 
