[normal] to enable the paramedics to do the assessment and convey that patient very appropriately to the specialist centre, be that a major trauma centre or a stroke centre. 
[normal]T
[normal]hat is the configuration that we are describing. So there is one thing around receiving, assessing and initiating treatment and either transferring
[normal],
